\description{
Monthly observations on 123 macroeconomic variables from the FRED-MD
database (McCracken and Ng, 2016), spanning January 1960 to December 2019
(720 months). Variables are transformed for stationarity using the
transformation codes listed in the online data appendix of the paper.
Covers output and income, labour market, consumption, housing,
inventories and orders, money and credit, interest rates, exchange rates,
and prices.
}
